# INInteractionDirection.unspecified

**Case**

An unspecified direction.

## Declaration

```swift
case unspecified
```

## Discussion

Choose this value for interactions that do not involve information moving onto or off of the device. This is the default value.

## Constants

- **INInteractionDirection.outgoing**: An interaction in which information is sent from the device.
- **INInteractionDirection.incoming**: An interaction in which information is received on the device.
